OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry at first
OL,6,Fover Shetland, otherwise it will be
OL,7,Fcloudy with patchy rain. The rain will
OL,8,Fturn more persistent and heavier
OL,9,Fovernight. Moderate southwesterly
OL,10,Fwinds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FA cloudy start with outbreaks
OL,13,Fof rain, then becoming dry through the
OL,14,Fmorning. Drier with sunny spells in
OL,15,Fthe afternoon.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FCool
OL,18,Fand breezy with sunshine and passing
OL,19,Fshowers on Tuesday. Dry with long
OL,20,Fbright or sunny spells on Wednesday
OL,21,Fand Thursday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
